{"tid":1607832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【晒你幾秒咋】十一齊屌TVB老母，每日洗版任務 - 喜療疤","createTime":"2019-10-01T04:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T07:41:59.000Z","uid":267969,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"51d4b2c30abd3c3733f22621e177d107f8e51951","tid":1607832,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各位marketing JJ注意，<br />\nTVB係品牌負資產，喺TVB落廣告，<br />\n你哋苦心經營嘅品牌形象將付諸流水！無人可憐！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTVB<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">幾日後</span></span>開始同廣告客戶傾下年合約，Keep住個氣勢到<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">年底</span></span>啦！<br />\n廣告界多番強調，去FB洗版係有用ga</strong> <br />\n<br />\n喜療疤喺黑心TVB賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，用完個傷口分分鐘發黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家出去發夢整親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一定轉用<span style=\"color: red;\">疤痕敵/唯一疤痕治</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />~<br />\n叫埋班夢遊朋友一齊抵制先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/71305228_463177494539105_1026712589238796288_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_eui2=AeEIUIRQwwOxXW3sRKIO0Yw1o_YANf0nmpMru-5NWX7hKUfyEJMBsp6RRZBSxCgl5oEjxfggvOfYkDE286qR7CrM7YS0NVcoV93KHqlOblP30Q&amp;_nc_oc=AQn3lLFcQv-Kc271cTpNGvF8jkFoW9OzeteVkm03QQKdflTEVYQcO97baWeem7nKB_k&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=6dbb5fe6796d6001a4115005d2b7772a&amp;oe=5DF1302A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F71305228_463177494539105_1026712589238796288_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_eui2%3DAeEIUIRQwwOxXW3sRKIO0Yw1o_YANf0nmpMru-5NWX7hKUfyEJMBsp6RRZBSxCgl5oEjxfggvOfYkDE286qR7CrM7YS0NVcoV93KHqlOblP30Q%26_nc_oc%3DAQn3lLFcQv-Kc271cTpNGvF8jkFoW9OzeteVkm03QQKdflTEVYQcO97baWeem7nKB_k%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D6dbb5fe6796d6001a4115005d2b7772a%26oe%3D5DF1302A&h=110672e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n是日精選@1 Oct 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>喜療疤</strong></span></span> <strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Hiruscar.family\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHiruscar.family&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=677e3b91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Hiruscar.family</a></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請用幾秒</span></strong>去派嬲、留言、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span></strong> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得?</span></strong>  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌只開行動post，順便follow埋<br />\n<br />\n <strong>※留言template，二擇其一，歡迎創意留言。</strong> <br />\n1️⃣<br />\n無綫新聞，助紂為虐，恥與為伍，撤回廣告！希望貴公司重新檢視你所僱用之廣告公司及其廣告計劃。貴公司有權選擇其他廣告公司，正如大眾同樣有權選擇你的競爭對手！<br />\n2️⃣<br />\n我本身好支持你哋公司嘅產品，奈何本人對貴公司於賣港媒體TVB落廣告此舉極為反感，決定罷買產品直至見唔到TVB 廣告為止。如果廣告部或者廣告公司hard sell 你買TVB，請考慮換咗廣告部同事或廣告公司！<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家用呢幅圖留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8J0Tr1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8J0Tr1F.jpg&h=b2a9cb2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark</span>: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</strong></span> <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=3ac65c64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a>  <br />\n －－－－－－－ <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請即follow:</span></strong> <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=491f39ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb<br />\nTG 抵制廣告行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=0d67dfef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 狙擊綜合頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2cctvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2cctvb&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=7a9b2efc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2cctvb</a>"},{"pid":"b320c0e615fd24cfbb989cfef3bc06cae2d88d83","tid":1607832,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:42:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有重要更新，請睇#2 回覆<br />\n<br />\n連登隨時死機，記得like我哋Facebook，獲得最新任務資訊</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8f605cf555b9a3449d0a2eeedea6eff6684dfb9b","tid":1607832,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:44:12.000Z","msg":"派完嬲出門口喇!~~~"},{"pid":"b875c97e01b62fc87c878033bd671b60007c4fcd","tid":1607832,"uid":164851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"賀佢老母"},{"pid":"c60d98570a077a1f11ac9c264fbd353b6183caa7"